snippet.title: MSX Longplay [048] PaRaDream (Homebrew)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Eino

AKA Parallel Dream. Turbo-R homebrew shooter developed by RAC House (1992). Graphics and sound are well done, although too cutesy for my taste. There's a Gradius style weapon selection at the beginning, but not much of a powerup system. Nothing particularly imaginative about level design or gameplay either. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
